# Snapshots — every dated YYYY-MM-DD/ directory is tracked (the
# daily-snapshot CI commits new ones; downstream Zenodo / citation
# tooling consumes them). Only working-state files inside snapshots/
# are excluded:
#   * .bak files from in-place audit-patch backups
#   * .parquet (transient analysis outputs)
# Bootstrap snapshot 2026-04-24/ is the legacy seed (kept for
# backward compatibility with any existing pinned-snapshot citations).
snapshots/**/*.bak
*.parquet
reports/
